    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six with its signature high-revving individual throttle bodies and Double VANOS variable valve timing. The chassis remains rigid, benefiting from documented subframe reinforcement and refreshed polyurethane bushings. The 6-speed Getrag manual transmission provides crisp engagement, paired with a factory-spec M-Variable limited-slip differential for optimal power delivery. While the finish shows honest patina consistent with spirited use, the drivetrain remains robust, delivering linear power up to a visceral 8,000 RPM redline. Suspension geometry is dialed in with upgraded Bilstein dampers, ensuring the precise turn-in and neutral balance this platform is renowned for.",
